NEW TRANSLATIONS

A new translation will be made available on LILYPOND.ORG as soon as a
useful part of the site has been translated, and is of good quality.

See the README file for the technical details of starting and
translating.

Note that contact.ihtml is the only .i[nclude]html to be translated,
news.ihtml and install/*.ihtml change too frequently.

The initial delivery of a translation for LILYPOND.ORG is about 3000 words.

Priorities:  1. delivery, 2. later, 3. optional, 4. not to be translated*)

1 about/index.html  --  http://lilypond.org/web/about/index.html
1 contact.ihtml  --  in http://lilypond.org/web/about/index.html and in http://lilypond.org/web/documentation.html
1 index.html  --  http://lilypond.org/web/index.html
